1. Ja ću *praviti* tortu za rođendan (I will make a cake for the birthday).
2. Oni su *pravili* kulu od peska na plaži (They were building a sandcastle on the beach).
3. Nemoj *praviti* gluposti! (Don't make silly things!)
4. Oni žele da *naprave* novu firmu (They want to start a new company).
5. Mama me uči kako se *pravi* pita sa jabukama (Mom is teaching me how to make an apple pie).
6. Kako se *pravi* kafa? (How to make coffee?)
7. Ona je *pravila* večeru dok sam ja bio u kupovini (She was making dinner while I was shopping).
8. Danas ćemo *praviti* čišćenje u kući (Today we will do cleaning in the house).
9. Oni su *pravili* zvukove dok je profesor pričao (They were making noises while the professor was talking).
10. Molim vas da *napravite* red u redu za karte (Please make a line for tickets).

Note: The word "praviti" means "to make" or "to create", while "napraviti" is a perfective form of the same verb, meaning "to have made" or "to create".